Jetpack Compose
Modern way to create Android UI without XML layout files
Everything (both UI and logic) is written in Kotlin
A single Kotlin file can contain both UI structure and behavior
Specifically focused on the UI toolkit aspect of app development



Jetpack Components
A collection of libraries (ViewModel, Room, Navigation, etc.)
Designed to solve various Android development challenges
Compatible with both approaches:
Traditional XML layouts with Views
Modern Compose UI
Helps maintain consistency whether you use XML or Compose